LoginUtils
----------

    python tools for logging in and out of an interface
    ===================================================


    completley secure, using a salted checksum, dont worry
    about storing user passwords in your database anymore


    
    Install & Usage Instructions:
    =============================

    to install
        python setup.py install

        or just

        pip install LoginUtils  

    to use:
        
        from LoginUtils import encrypt_password, check_password

        pw = encrypt_password('agoodpw')
        check_password('agoodpw',pw) => True
